在9世纪，海盗和奴隶贩子将捕捉的外国人在中国销售作为奴隶。<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=jqAGIL02BWQC&pg=PA44&dq=luxury+commerce+horde+of+pirates+yellow+sea+protests+of+the+governments+of+the+korean&hl=en&ei=i28vTdrCE4et8Aarg4X2CQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCMQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=female%20luxury%20commerce%20horde%20of%20pirates%20yellow%20sea%20protests%20of%20the%20governments%20of%20the%20korean&f=false|title=The golden peaches of Samarkand: a study of Tʻang exotics|author=Edward H. Schafer|year=1963|publisher=University of California Press|location=|isbn=0-520-05462-8|page=44|accessdate=2011-01-09|archive-date=2013-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130604023730/http://books.google.com/books?id=jqAGIL02BWQC&pg=PA44&dq=luxury+commerce+horde+of+pirates+yellow+sea+protests+of+the+governments+of+the+korean&hl=en&ei=i28vTdrCE4et8Aarg4X2CQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCMQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=female%20luxury%20commerce%20horde%20of%20pirates%20yellow%20sea%20protests%20of%20the%20governments%20of%20the%20korean&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Jang Bogo">{{cite web|url=http://100.naver.com/100.nhn?docid=132849 |title=장보고 |publisher= Naver/Doosan Encyclopedia |language=ko |accessdate= }}</ref>由于这一结果，朝鲜海军将军張保皐在清海镇驻军，將中国海盗趕离朝鲜西部海岸。<ref name="Jang Bogo"/>

